<p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241125/1732544762801049547.png" title="1732544762801049547.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-11-25 222450.png" width="790" height="516" style="width: 790px; height: 516px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">为深入领悟红色家书中蕴含的革命精神与崇高情怀，进一步坚定入党积极分子的信仰与追求。经济管理学院第31期入党积极分子学班于2024年11月20日18时，在A10-315教室开展以“继承革命精神--读红色家书有感”为主题的集体学习，班长李宵云领学。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><strong>学习课堂</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><strong><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241125/1732544870544038064.jpg" title="1732544870544038064.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241125222527.jpg" width="791" height="653" style="width: 791px; height: 653px;"/></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">本次集体学习，李宵云首先就红色家书的内涵本质进行了简介，随后从“传承为党为国的忠诚”、“传承敢为人先,发扬不惧牺牲”、“传承功成不必在我,功成必定有我”三个角度来阐述新时代中国青年应有的忠诚、责任与担当。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241125/1732544970489081243.png" title="1732544970489081243.png" alt="微信图片_20241125222536.png" width="796" height="601" style="width: 796px; height: 601px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">在这次集体学习中，各入党积极分子了解到，红色家书不仅是历史的见证，更是革命精神的传承，它们记录了革命者们的信仰、决心和牺牲，是中华民族革命精神的重要体现。新时代中国青年要从跨越时空的红色家书中汲取智慧和力量，以实际行动积极传承红色基因，赓续红色血脉，用坚定的理想信念.砥砺对党的赤诚忠心，筑牢信仰之基、补足精神之钙、把稳思想之舵。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><strong>心得分享</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><strong><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241125/1732545084053026250.png" title="1732545084053026250.png" alt="微信图片_20241125222553.png" width="801" height="577" style="width: 801px; height: 577px;"/></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">在历史的长河中，总有一些人，他们用生命诠释了信仰，用热血书写了忠诚，他们的名字或许已被岁月尘封，但他们的精神却如同璀璨星辰，永远照亮着后人前行的道路。我从一封封红色家书汲取了无尽的力量与深刻的启示。这些家书不仅是对家人的深情嘱托，更是对党和人民事业的坚定承诺。作为新时代的青年，我们要继承和发扬这种精神，将其转化为推动社会进步、实现个人价值的强大动力，为实现中华民族伟大复兴的中国梦贡献青春力量。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;--B230505 万俊豪</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241125/1732545159587043658.png" title="1732545159587043658.png" alt="微信图片_20241125222559.png" width="827" height="638" style="width: 827px; height: 638px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">在新时代的征程上，继承和发扬革命精神是我们每一个中国人的责任和使命。通过学习，我更加坚定了理想信念，在快速发展的现代社会，我们也需要不断学习新知识，适应新变化，勇于自我革命，不断提升自己的综合素质。在新时代，我们要继承和发扬团结协作的精神，共同为实现国家的宏伟目标而努力，将以革命先烈为榜样，不忘初心，牢记使命，为实现中华民族的伟大复兴贡献自己的力量。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; --B230501 付晶菁</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241125/1732545226225031401.png" title="1732545226225031401.png" alt="微信图片_20241125222605.png" width="826" height="641" style="width: 826px; height: 641px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">革命精神如晨曦初露，照亮了我们入党积极分子的心田。集体学习的时刻，仿佛历史与现实交织，我们共同探寻着革命精神的璀璨光芒。走进那段烽火岁月，我仿佛看到了革命先辈们英勇奋斗的身影。他们怀揣着坚定的信仰，不畏艰难险阻，用鲜血和生命书写了壮丽的篇章。这份精神，如同璀璨的星辰，永远闪耀在我们心中，它激励着我们不断前行，不断超越自我。作为入党积极分子，我们有责任也有义务将这份精神传承下去，让它在新的时代焕发出更加绚丽的光彩。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;--B230507 刘恋</span></p><p><br/></p>